  <entry>
    <title>miniOb 源码阅读笔记</title>
    <link href="/2024/09/26/oceanbase/"/>
    <url>/2024/09/26/oceanbase/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="miniOb-源码阅读笔记"><a href="#miniOb-源码阅读笔记" class="headerlink" title="miniOb 源码阅读笔记"></a>miniOb 源码阅读笔记</h2><p>官方文档：<a href="https://www.oceanbase.com/docs/-developer-quickstart-10000000000627360">https://www.oceanbase.com/docs/-developer-quickstart-10000000000627360</a></p><h3 id="完善基本命令-drop-table-来梳理一条基本的-SQL-语句的生命历程"><a href="#完善基本命令-drop-table-来梳理一条基本的-SQL-语句的生命历程" class="headerlink" title="完善基本命令 drop table 来梳理一条基本的 SQL 语句的生命历程"></a>完善基本命令 drop table 来梳理一条基本的 SQL 语句的生命历程</h3><p><img src="/./miniob_img/SQL%E5%B1%82%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6.png" alt="alt text" title="SQL层整体框架"></p><h4 id="Parser-模块"><a href="#Parser-模块" class="headerlink" title="Parser 模块"></a>Parser 模块</h4><p>当一条 SQL 请求到达 Server 端后，首先经过的是 Parser 模块。Parser 模块主要作用是根据定义的语法规则判断一条 SQL 语句的格式是否符合对应的语法结构，<strong>将一条用户写的 SQL 请求转换成可以在数据库内核中所使用的数据结构</strong>。</p><p><strong><code>miniob/src/observer/net/sql_task_handler.cpp</code></strong> 文件中定义了一个函数 <code>RC SqlTaskHandler::handle_sql(SQLStageEvent *sql_event)</code>，这个函数的前身目前并未研究。函数内部会依次调用<code>query_cache_stage_</code>，<code>parse_stage_</code>，<code>resolve_stage_</code>，<code>optimize_stage_</code>，<code>execute_stage_</code>五个函数，用于处理 SQL 语句的五个主要生命节点。</p><p>对于 Parse 模块:</p><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs kotlin">rc = parse_stage_.handle_request(sql_event);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (OB_FAIL(rc)) &#123;<br>    LOG_TRACE(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;failed to do parse. rc=%s&quot;</span>, strrc(rc));<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> rc;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- ![alt text](./miniob_img/001.png) --><p>会调用 <code>parse_stage_(class ParseStage)</code>中的<code>handle_request</code>方法来处理该阶段。至于函数的具体实现先跳过，直接用官方文档的话：</p><blockquote><p>一条 SQL 语句，无论写得多么复杂，本质上就是一层一层嵌套的树状结构。Parser 模块这一个部分主要做的就是根据用户所写的语法规则正确的识别，并将一条 SQL 语句转化为一个语法树的结构。但一条符合语法树规则的 SQL 不一定是一条“合格”的 SQL，数据库中还存在着许多约束，一条 SQL 还必须满足语义的约束，许多语法的约束以及虚视图的展开都是在 Resolver 模块中完成的。</p></blockquote><h4 id="Resolver-模块"><a href="#Resolver-模块" class="headerlink" title="Resolver 模块"></a>Resolver 模块</h4><p>Resolver 模块主要作用是对 Parser 模块所生成的符合语法规则的树状结构进行进一步的约束检查，还可能会提取表达式的属性。<br>在 Resolver 这一层会转化成一个自己的数据结构。在 OceanBase 中用的是 STMT（Statement），这是非常重要的一个类。</p><p>对于 Resolver 模块:</p><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs kotlin">rc = resolve_stage_.handle_request(sql_event);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (OB_FAIL(rc)) &#123;<br>    LOG_TRACE(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;failed to do resolve. rc=%s&quot;</span>, strrc(rc));<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> rc;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- ![alt text](./miniob_img/002.png) --><p>会调用 <code>resolver_stage_(class ResolverStage)</code>中的<code>handle_request</code>方法来处理该阶段。<br>函数内部会创建 STMT 类，用于后续的处理。</p><h4 id="STMT-类浅析"><a href="#STMT-类浅析" class="headerlink" title="STMT 类浅析"></a>STMT 类浅析</h4><p>SQL 语句解析后通过 Resolver 转换成 Stmt，Stmt 中定义了一系列操作类型<code>StmtType</code>，其中包括需要完善的 DROP_TABLE。</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs scss"><span class="hljs-selector-id">#define</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM</span>()            \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(CALC)         \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(SELECT)       \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(INSERT)       \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(UPDATE)       \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(DELETE)       \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(CREATE_TABLE) \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(DROP_TABLE)   \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(CREATE_INDEX) \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(DROP_INDEX)   \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(SYNC)         \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(SHOW_TABLES)  \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(DESC_TABLE)   \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(BEGIN)        \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(COMMIT)       \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(ROLLBACK)     \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(LOAD_DATA)    \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(HELP)         \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(EXIT)         \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(EXPLAIN)      \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(PREDICATE)    \<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(SET_VARIABLE)<br><br>enum class StmtType<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-selector-id">#define</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM</span>(name) name,<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DEFINE_ENUM</span>()<br><span class="hljs-selector-id">#undef</span> DEFINE_ENUM_ITEM<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- ![alt text](./miniob_img/003.png) --><p>在文件夹<code>miniob/src/observer/sql/stmt</code>中，有各种<code>StmtType</code>对应的处理类，源码中并没有添加<code>drop_tables_stmt</code>对应的处理类和处理函数，先创建文件：<br><img src="/./miniob_img/004.png" alt="alt text"><br><code>Stmt</code>类中定义了<code>create_stmt</code>函数，函数会根据<code>sql_node.flag</code>来决定创建哪个具体的<code>Stmt</code>类，在函数中的 switch 中添加属于<code>drop table</code>对应的 case。</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">case SCF_DROP_TABLE: &#123;<br>    return DropTableStmt::<span class="hljs-built_in">create</span>(db, sql_node.drop_table, stmt);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>头文件定义类<code>DropTableStmt</code>，继承<code>Stmt</code>类，具体实现如下：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">pragma</span> once</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;sql/stmt/stmt.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Db</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @brief 表示删除表的语句</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @ingroup Statement</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @details 虽然解析成了stmt，但是与原始的SQL解析后的数据也差不多</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DropTableStmt</span> : <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Stmt<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">DropTableStmt</span>(<span class="hljs-type">const</span> std::string &amp;table_name) : <span class="hljs-built_in">table_name_</span>(table_name) &#123;&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">virtual</span> ~<span class="hljs-built_in">DropTableStmt</span>() = <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>;<br>  <span class="hljs-function">StmtType <span class="hljs-title">type</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">override</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> StmtType::DROP_TABLE; &#125;<br><br>  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> std::string &amp;<span class="hljs-title">table_name</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> table_name_; &#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">static</span> RC          <span class="hljs-title">create</span><span class="hljs-params">(Db *db, <span class="hljs-type">const</span> DropTableSqlNode &amp;drop_table, Stmt *&amp;stmt)</span></span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">private</span>:<br>  std::string table_name_;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>DropTableStmt</code>类声明了 create 函数，同时删除表格需要表格的名称，故还需要表示表格名称的属性<code>table_name_</code>。<br>函数的实现如下：</p><figure class="highlight zephir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs zephir">RC DropTableStmt::create(Db *db, <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> DropTableSqlNode &amp;drop_table, Stmt *&amp;stmt)<br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!db-&gt;find_table(drop_table.relation_name.c_str())) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> RC::SCHEMA_TABLE_NOT_EXIST;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    stmt = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> DropTableStmt(drop_table.relation_name);<br>    sql_debug(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;drop table statement: table name %s&quot;</span>,    drop_table.relation_name.c_str());<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> RC::SUCCESS;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>函数主要创建了一个<code>DropTableStmt</code>对象，并传入了删除表格的名称。<strong>至此，成功创建了一个删除表格对应的<code>Stmt</code>对象</strong>。</p><h4 id="Optimizer-模块"><a href="#Optimizer-模块" class="headerlink" title="Optimizer 模块"></a>Optimizer 模块</h4>]]></content>
    
    
    
